    "bbox": [
      58.34,
      568.07,
      531.65,
      608.93
    ],
    "text": "Showers or thundershowers may occur at a few places in Western and Sabaragamuwa provinces and in Galle, Matara, Kandy and Nuwara-Eliya districts after 2.00 pm.",
